
Zen Laptop Store
Zen Laptop Store is a responsive and feature-rich e-commerce web application built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, designed to provide users with an easy and interactive online laptop shopping experience.

Features
Responsive Design:
Ensures optimal usability across devices.

Product Pages:

Display a catalog of laptops with filters for price, brand, and specifications.
Individual product pages showcasing detailed information and images.
User Authentication:

Registration and login functionality with form validation.
Admin Panel:

Add, edit, and manage product listings.
Shopping Cart and Checkout:

Review selected items and proceed to checkout seamlessly.
Technologies Used
Frontend:

HTML
CSS / SCSS
JavaScript


Fonts for styling.
Images for products and design elements.
How to Use
Clone the Repository:

bash
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/your-username/zen-laptop-store.git  
Run the Application:

Open index.html in your browser to view the site.
For Backend Features:

Set up a local PHP server (e.g., XAMPP, WAMP).
Place the project files in the server's root directory.
Future Enhancements
Integrate a database for dynamic content management.
Add a secure payment gateway.
Implement a search bar and AI-based recommendations.
Contribution
Contributions, issues, and feature requests are welcome! Feel free to open a pull request or file an issue.

